Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.75,0:00:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向往天空 亲近天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.14,0:00:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翱翔于天空的神秘力量开始被一少部分人掌握的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.85,0:00:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guardian
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.25,0:00:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有一个传说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.55,0:00:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在天之边际云之彼方存在着一片黄金之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.72,0:00:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个故事讲述了一个追寻梦想自由生存的天空盗贼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.51,0:00:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空盗团少年——酷的波澜起伏的爱和冒险的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.61,0:02:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了了结一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.10,0:02:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有与酷分开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.61,0:02:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让苦恼的蕾绽放笑容的却正是酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.84,0:02:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷和蕾决定不逃避现实 一起去煌珠乐园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.59,0:02:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一方面希丝卡在两人身上看到了希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.80,0:02:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了新的行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.53,0:02:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲开ChaosChoir\N的追击后继续踏上旅途的酷他们的前方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.26,0:02:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无限神秘的煌珠乐园展现在眼前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.60,0:02:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.59,0:02:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开酷他们的希丝卡独自返回守护翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.24,0:03:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着说服上层避免与煌珠乐园全面开战的使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.17,0:03:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为完全保护协会的守护翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.01,0:03:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挑起与本该保护的煌珠之间的战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.23,0:03:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是决不应该的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.78,0:03:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何也要阻止这场战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.13,0:03:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管起因是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.30,0:03:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克鲁斯辅佐官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.72,0:03:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事要汇报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.99,0:03:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二十三唱 约定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.33,0:03:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.72,0:03:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去没什么精神啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.33,0:03:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过不要紧的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.89,0:03:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都走到这里了只需最后再加把劲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.12,0:03:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.21,0:03:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.37,0:04:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什么啊 突然道谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.00,0:04:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能走到这里是因为有酷在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.46,0:04:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有酷的话我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.83,0:04:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.90,0:04:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是约定了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.87,0:04:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“带蕾去煌珠乐园”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.47,0:04:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能遇到酷真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.08,0:04:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.81,0:04:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在 在干什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.77,0:04:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.30,0:04:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守护翼和ChaosChoir
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.41,0:04:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据内部消息守护翼是发动总攻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.10,0:05:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说真的打算和ChaosChoir开战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.63,0:05:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是说这话的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.23,0:05:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.21,0:05:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.92,0:05:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.10,0:05:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉撒蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.92,0:05:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.46,0:05:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.39,0:05:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.22,0:05:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家冷静
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.99,0:05:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重整阵列
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.91,0:05:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.65,0:06:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 在干什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.33,0:06:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人攻过来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.20,0:06:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.06,0:07:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.80,0:07:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.86,0:07:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次见到伊芙大人这副样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.12,0:07:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊芙大人知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.32,0:07:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾芙丽·梅札兰斯大人就在附近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.21,0:07:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 欧珐斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.15,0:07:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然不郑重出迎是不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.12,0:07:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话情况很糟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.58,0:07:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞空艇部队全灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.63,0:07:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地面部队也是ChaosChoir方面惯于作战的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.33,0:07:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是战斗力还是指挥能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.02,0:07:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一边倒地处于劣势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.93,0:07:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉撒蒂你们为什么会来这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.45,0:07:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守护翼发动总攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.09,0:07:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能战斗的都被驱使参军了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.12,0:07:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话我也不想战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.64,0:08:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 守护翼曾经保护我 对我有恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.15,0:08:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然姐姐要战斗那我也一起战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.31,0:08:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能待在姐姐身边我就能奋战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.76,0:08:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么想了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.65,0:08:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.14,0:08:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煌珠互相厮杀真的很痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.59,0:08:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.57,0:08:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ChaosChoir的战斗方式太没人性了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.43,0:08:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们将煌珠用完就抛弃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.61,0:08:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果丧失战斗能力的话就像废物一样抛弃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.88,0:08:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐也不能原谅做出这种事的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.80,0:08:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是敌人一个接一个地出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.29,0:08:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都已经到极限了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.22,0:08:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们接下来不知道会怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.37,0:09:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 莉莉雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.47,0:09:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.62,0:09:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.44,0:09:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.43,0:09:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.99,0:09:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们前来迎接您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.79,0:09:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾芙丽·梅札兰斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.41,0:09:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想制止战争吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.26,0:09:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.40,0:09:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不知道她去哪儿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.17,0:09:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她刚才在河边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.83,0:09:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 谢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.75,0:10:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想制止这场战争吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.78,0:10:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你来我们这边的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.09,0:10:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都将结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.61,0:10:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.11,0:10:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我去煌珠乐园的话...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.37,0:10:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.56,0:10:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝与我{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.00,0:10:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情分已尽{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.48,0:10:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铺路向宫{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.16,0:10:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气息相应{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.54,0:10:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉沉睡去{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.80,0:10:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.25,0:10:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于我手中{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.59,0:10:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不再延续{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.65,0:10:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.71,0:10:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.73,0:11:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.74,0:11:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.51,0:11:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.30,0:11:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们对蕾做了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.13,0:11:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也听到了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.23,0:11:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾芙丽·梅札兰斯大人也自愿选择来我们这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.21,0:11:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.71,0:11:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾不可能那么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.71,0:11:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.18,0:11:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.46,0:11:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.38,0:11:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卧鲁克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.36,0:11:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把蕾还给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.51,0:11:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之去处{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.78,0:11:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许阻拦{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.18,0:11:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速速退下{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.91,0:11:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.97,0:12:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.28,0:12:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.10,0:12:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.77,0:12:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.61,0:12:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你既是蕾的同契者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.88,0:12:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就该理解她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.38,0:12:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是为了制止战争才独自前往的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.10,0:12:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为敌人的目标是蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.37,0:12:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而她也知道这一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.58,0:12:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这你知道的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.11,0:12:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想再让谁受伤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.79,0:12:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么想了那孩子才...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.35,0:12:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.21,0:12:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾不想战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.90,0:12:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总考虑着想做点什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.72,0:12:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 但是我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.07,0:12:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.21,0:13:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被煌珠抛弃的同契者啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.87,0:13:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.50,0:13:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.41,0:13:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卧鲁说的没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.73,0:13:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被搭档抛弃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.10,0:13:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太丢人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.94,0:13:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.27,0:13:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么就算无需战斗也愿相伴一生的是谁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.99,0:13:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如果对七煌宝树死心了的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.36,0:13:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有我去夺回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.19,0:13:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.17,0:13:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不中听的话就好好保护她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.44,0:13:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管对手是我还是他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.05,0:13:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.00,0:13:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦的不止是你一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.77,0:13:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卧鲁他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.08,0:13:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别多嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.86,0:13:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 对不起啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.41,0:14:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这里的目的可能落空了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.03,0:14:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七煌宝树既然已经去了煌珠乐园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.60,0:14:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场战争也就快结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.25,0:14:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.29,0:14:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.40,0:14:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,福音的最终乐章还没响起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.36,0:14:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.99,0:14:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是个令人不爽的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.81,0:14:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我和他意见一致
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.76,0:14:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉撒蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.41,0:14:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样子不像你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.04,0:14:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所认识的酷德·望·朱鲁爱特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.14,0:14:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还未想好就已行动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.50,0:14:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这是在做什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.53,0:14:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明很理解酷的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.33,0:15:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我也理解蕾的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.89,0:15:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是她决定的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.27,0:15:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想成全她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.54,0:15:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为一名煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.81,0:15:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面等待着的会是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.54,0:15:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都生活了几百年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.42,0:15:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该已经习惯这种事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.21,0:15:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么心绪如此不宁呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.05,0:15:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.32,0:15:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是酷和蕾吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.58,0:15:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷和蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.24,0:15:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉两人相遇之后萌生了很多很多的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.73,0:15:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以那两人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.59,0:15:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.39,0:15:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能制止这场战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.20,0:15:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.34,0:15:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带来一个全新的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.61,0:15:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么想了大家才赶到这里来的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.46,0:16:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您醒了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.49,0:16:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来战争就将结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.55,0:16:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后开始一个新的时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.70,0:16:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能遇到酷真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.62,0:16:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.04,0:16:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.27,0:17:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.94,0:17:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.89,0:17:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.95,0:17:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙在干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.50,0:17:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.39,0:17:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.03,0:17:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉撒蒂 莉莉雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.72,0:17:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.40,0:17:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已抓住蕾的现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.16,0:17:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫌同契者碍事是理所当然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.65,0:17:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里交给我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.30,0:17:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.99,0:17:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.73,0:17:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.59,0:17:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终结的福音响起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.04,0:17:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卧鲁克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.96,0:17:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还真不知道居然有猎人不是为钱而战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.32,0:17:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为我而战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.74,0:17:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅此而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.99,0:18:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.11,0:18:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷 没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.71,0:18:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你死了的话就没脸见蕾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.48,0:18:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.66,0:18:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命硬的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.12,0:18:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.00,0:18:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定去蕾的所在之处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.13,0:18:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.29,0:18:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定至死也不离开蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.01,0:18:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.08,0:18:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就看我的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.73,0:18:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.54,0:19:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能飞吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.26,0:19:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撞得很厉害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.26,0:19:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过应该能行吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.79,0:19:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避开 龙威
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.32,0:19:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.30,0:19:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞船稳定不下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.42,0:20:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们所开创的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.36,0:20:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我见识见识吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.28,0:20:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卧鲁 后面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.79,0:20:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.60,0:20:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煌珠必须由我们管辖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.96,0:20:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不明白这一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.46,0:20:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奉命拘捕你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.10,0:20:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须消灭他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.77,0:20:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪恶的并不只是他一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.42,0:20:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐惧煌珠的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.88,0:20:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宣扬人类至上的思想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.08,0:20:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤害着煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.78,0:20:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后刀戈相向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.62,0:20:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们守护者必须一肩承担的罪孽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.23,0:20:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.29,0:20:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.50,0:20:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们一定...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.91,0:21:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙 龙威
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.25,0:21:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.42,0:21:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是约好了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.02,0:21:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带酷和蕾去煌珠乐园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.49,0:21:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到蕾后就不要再分开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.11,0:21:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.24,0:21:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着我 蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.55,0:21:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.65,0:22:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有着和平的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.59,0:22:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在只剩下悲伤和愤怒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.42,0:22:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 煌珠乐园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.43,0:23:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二十四唱 煌珠乐园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.70,0:23:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而少年的生命到头了
